<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 13:08:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>卡尔·施罗德：奇点是一个古老的想法。继续前进！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/karl-schroeder-the-singularity-is-an-old-idea-keep-moving-forward</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/karl-schroeder-the-singularity-is-an-old-idea-keep-moving-forward.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 13:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/karl-schroeder-the-singularity-is-an-old-idea-keep-moving-forward</guid></item><item><title>宇宙是计算出来的吗？ |萨拉·沃克和莱克斯·弗里德曼</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-the-universe-a-computation-sara-walker-and-lex-fridman</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-the-universe-a-computation-sara-walker-and-lex-fridman</guid></item><item><title>宇宙的大部分都缺失了。科学家认为他们可能已经找到了</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-large-amount-of-the-universe-is-missing-scientists-think-they-may-have-found-it</link><description>一定有一些我们看不到的额外质量——天文学家称之为“暗物质” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-large-amount-of-the-universe-is-missing-scientists-think-they-may-have-found-it2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-large-amount-of-the-universe-is-missing-scientists-think-they-may-have-found-it</guid></item><item><title>肠脑肌肉轴：神经肌肉衰老和认知衰弱的微生物调节</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-gutbrainmuscle-axis-microbial-regulation-of-neuromuscular-aging-and-cognitive-frailty</link><description>认知衰弱以身体虚弱和认知障碍并存为特征，已成为老龄化人口面临的主要挑战，并且与肌肉减少症、神经退行性变和慢性炎症密切相关。越来越多的证据表明，肠道微生物群通过整合肠道-大脑-肌肉轴，充当神经肌肉和神经认知衰老的中央调节器。这篇综述强调了微生物失调、短链脂肪酸 (SCFA) 产生减少、全身性内毒素血症和微生物代谢物改变如何导致线粒体功能障碍、神经炎症、合成代谢抵抗和神经可塑性受损。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-gutbrainmuscle-axis-microbial-regulation-of-neuromuscular-aging-and-cognitive-frailty2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-gutbrainmuscle-axis-microbial-regulation-of-neuromuscular-aging-and-cognitive-frailty</guid></item><item><title>二尖瓣脱垂患者运动时室性心律失常</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ventricular-arrhythmias-during-exercise-in-patients-with-mitral-valve-prolapse</link><description>背景 二尖瓣脱垂 (MVP) 可能与室性心律失常 (VA) 相关，但人们对这些患者的 VA 与运动之间的关系知之甚少。本研究的目的是评估 MVP 患者运动测试中 VA 的发生情况及其严重程度，并探讨运动中 VA 与随访期间心律失常事件发生之间的关联。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ventricular-arrhythmias-during-exercise-in-patients-with-mitral-valve-prolapse.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 12:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ventricular-arrhythmias-during-exercise-in-patients-with-mitral-valve-prolapse</guid></item><item><title>运动映射以实现环周弥漫性神经胶质瘤的切除</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/motor-mapping-to-enable-resections-of-perirolandic-diffuse-gliomas-neurooncology</link><description>术中运动映射对于最大程度地安全至关重要&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/motor-mapping-to-enable-resections-of-perirolandic-diffuse-gliomas-neurooncology2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 11:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/motor-mapping-to-enable-resections-of-perirolandic-diffuse-gliomas-neurooncology</guid></item><item><title>慢波睡眠碎片化治疗觉醒和睡眠相关的过度运动性癫痫</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/slowwave-sleep-fragmentation-in-disorders-of-arousal-and-sleeprelated-hypermotor-epilepsy</link><description>该网站使用安全服务来防范恶意机器人。当网站验证您不是机器人时会显示此页面。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/slowwave-sleep-fragmentation-in-disorders-of-arousal-and-sleeprelated-hypermotor-epilepsy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/slowwave-sleep-fragmentation-in-disorders-of-arousal-and-sleeprelated-hypermotor-epilepsy</guid></item><item><title>癌症有效过继细胞免疫疗法的标志和相关性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/hallmarks-and-correlates-of-effective-adoptive-cell-immunotherapy-for-cancer</link><description>在这篇综述中，Krishna 及其同事利用过去二十年的临床和科学进展，描述了在使用肿瘤浸润淋巴细胞和 TCR 工程 T 细胞疗法进行过继细胞治疗期间影响临床结果的许多因素。他们解释了 T 细胞内在因素和肿瘤特异性因素如何在患有晚期癌症的患者中促进过继细胞移植 (ACT) 的成功，并概述了 ACT 领域的新方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hallmarks-and-correlates-of-effective-adoptive-cell-immunotherapy-for-cancer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 11:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/hallmarks-and-correlates-of-effective-adoptive-cell-immunotherapy-for-cancer</guid></item><item><title>科学家可能找到了延长小鼠生育能力的方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-may-have-found-a-way-to-extend-fertility-in-mice</link><description>随着卵巢老化，它们的支持组织变得更僵硬，减缓这一过程可能是延长生育能力的关键。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-may-have-found-a-way-to-extend-fertility-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 11:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-may-have-found-a-way-to-extend-fertility-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>与宫内节育器和口服避孕药使用相关的卵巢癌肿瘤免疫特征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ovarian-cancer-tumor-immune-profiles-associated-with-intrauterine-device-and-oral-contraceptive-use</link><description>蒙焦维，JM，巴比奇，A.，笹本，N. &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ovarian-cancer-tumor-